OL,4,CDepartment for Education had no Covid
OL,5,Cplan, say MPs
OL,6, A group of MPs has said that the
OL,7, Department for Education (DfE) had "no
OL,8, plan" to deal with the Covid pandemic.
OL,10,FA report by the Public Accounts
OL,11,FCommittee (PAC) says that the DfE
OL,12,Fstruggled to react to events in a
OL,13,Ftimely and effective way in England.
OL,15,FIt says the failure to set standards
OL,16,Ffor in-school and remote learning meant
OL,17,Fchildren "had very unequal experiences"
OL,18,Fduring the pandemic.
OL,20,FIn response, the DfE says it acted
OL,21,Fswiftly and provided extensive support.
